Then there=E2=80=99s Trump=E2=80=99s would-be F.B.I. director, Kash Patel, =
who comes armed with an enemies list but little in the way of credentials. =
There were encouraging signs for Kash today when Sen. John Cornyn said ( ht=
tps://www.politico.com/live-updates/2024/12/05/congress/kash-patel-fbi-corn=
yn-00192805?utm_campaign=3DThe+Best+%26+The+Brightest+-+SUBSCRIBERS+%2812%2=
F5%2F24%29&utm_content=3DThe+Best+%26+The+Brightest+-+SUBSCRIBERS+%2812%2F3=
%2F24%29&utm_medium=3Demail_action&utm_source=3Dcustomer.io&utm_term=3Df6c6=
0617da42abd12a ) on the Hugh Hewitt Show that =E2=80=9Che will=E2=80=9D be =
confirmed to lead the bureau. On the other hand, it=E2=80=99s still early, =
and everyone=E2=80=99s been a bit too distracted with other noms to fully f=
ocus on Patel. Within the bureau, the reaction to Patel=E2=80=99s selection=
 is decidedly mixed, according to a
recently retired senior official at the F.B.I. Most F.B.I. officers and age=
nts are politically conservative, like many in law enforcement, this person=
 noted, and many would welcome a shake-up=E2=80=94especially one that empow=
ers field offices at the expense of D.C., where then-director Robert Muelle=
r centralized many functions in the wake of 9/11.

But relocating key F.B.I. functions outside the capital is actually among t=
he least controversial of Patel=E2=80=99s proposals for the agency. He=E2=
=80=99s also vowed to prosecute political opponents and members of the medi=
a, and to fashion himself as a sort of blunt weapon of Trump=E2=80=99s camp=
aign of retribution. I=E2=80=99m already hearing justifications from some T=
rump allies, who note that the Obama administration did indeed ( https://fr=
eedom.press/issues/obama-used-espionage-act-put-record-number-reporters-sou=
rces-jail-and-trump-could-be-even-worse/?utm_campaign=3DThe+Best+%26+The+Br=
ightest+-+SUBSCRIBERS+%2812%2F5%2F24%29&utm_content=3DThe+Best+%26+The+Brig=
htest+-+SUBSCRIBERS+%2812%2F3%2F24%29&utm_medium=3Demail_action&utm_source=
=3Dcustomer.io&utm_term=3Df6c60617da42abd12a ) put record numbers of leaker=
s in prison and investigated but never prosecuted multiple journalists. The=
 recently retired F.B.I. official speculated that Patel and Trump=E2=80=99s=
 new choice for attorney general, Pam Bondi, would
investigate select leaks, and potentially subpoena reporters.

Even so, there=E2=80=99s plenty there to make Republican senators second-gu=
ess the wisdom of putting Patel in charge of federal law enforcement. (Reme=
mber, it only takes four senators to kill a nomination=E2=80=94and Susan Co=
llins, Lisa Murkowski, and Mitch McConnell are just a few of several wild c=
ards ( https://puck.news/will-the-senate-actually-confirm-pete-hegseth/?utm=
_campaign=3DThe+Best+%26+The+Brightest+-+SUBSCRIBERS+%2812%2F5%2F24%29&utm_=
content=3DThe+Best+%26+The+Brightest+-+SUBSCRIBERS+%2812%2F3%2F24%29&utm_me=
dium=3Demail_action&utm_source=3Dcustomer.io&utm_term=3Df6c60617da42abd12a =
), as my partner Abby Livingston has reported.) That may take the pressure =
off the later round of Trump allies who will have to face the Senate, such =
as Heather Nauert, who served as Trump=E2=80=99s acting undersecretary of s=
tate for public diplomacy and public affairs and is now being considered fo=
r a foreign policy position. (Nauert withdrew from consideration to be Trum=
p=E2=80=99s ambassador to the U.N., in 2019, when
it was revealed that she=E2=80=99d employed a nanny without the proper visa=
 a decade prior=E2=80=94a scandal that seems positively quaint by 2024 stan=
dards.)

Others are hanging around the hoop, waiting for a second or third round of =
cabinet flameouts to make their move. To wit: I=E2=80=99m told that Ric Gre=
nell, Trump=E2=80=99s former acting director of national intelligence and a=
mbassador to Germany, who has lobbied for a
decade to be secretary of state, turned down an offer to serve as special e=
nvoy for resolving the Russia-Ukraine conflict. An ally familiar with his t=
hinking said he didn=E2=80=99t want to look like a =E2=80=9Csquish=E2=80=9D=
 to the MAGA base. Instead, I=E2=80=99m told, he plans to remain in Trump=
=E2=80=99s orbit and wait for Rubio to crash back to earth.

